00:08:58.400 --> 00:09:02.240
MARGARET GARCIA:
I think if you're

00:09:02.240 --> 00:09:13.820
looking at the Mexican history,
obviously there's racism.

00:09:13.820 --> 00:09:17.840
They're not looking at white
people to say, you know,

00:09:17.840 --> 00:09:24.260
