here or whatever they're doing.

00:09:24.260 --> 00:09:27.020
And I'm not sure if
I'm making sense.

00:09:27.020 --> 00:09:30.734
You know, back in the '30s, they
literally just went into places

00:09:30.734 --> 00:09:32.150
and if you were
Mexican, it didn't

00:09:32.150 --> 00:09:34.400
matter if you were born here
or you weren't born here.

00:09:34.400 --> 00:09:35.780
They didn't look at your papers.

00:09:35.780 --> 00:09:38.570
They just rounded people
up on cattle cars,

00:09:38.570 --> 00:09:42.320
like my uncle and
his two sisters.

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:48.440
My father's cousins
were literally

00:09:48.440 --> 00:09:52.370
rounded up out of first and
second grade and kindergarten,

00:09:52.370 --> 00:09:55.320
put on an open cattle
car with their father--

00:09:55.320 --> 00:09:58.700
