as well as their mother--

00:09:58.700 --> 00:10:01.520
and put on that open
cattle car where it rained

00:10:01.520 --> 00:10:04.370
and they were shipped all the
way down to central Mexico

00:10:04.370 --> 00:10:06.950
to make it hard
for them to return.

00:10:06.950 --> 00:10:10.550
And they sat in that open
cattle car for days, you know,

00:10:10.550 --> 00:10:16.460
shivering and not being
fed and disposed of.

00:10:16.460 --> 00:10:23.090
There was no compassion for
them or their status at all.

00:10:23.090 --> 00:10:25.010
MARCUS GRIMALDO: And
this was in the--

00:10:25.010 --> 00:10:26.369
