you're lesser than human to say

00:11:31.220 --> 00:11:34.340
they're taking
something from us.

00:11:34.340 --> 00:11:38.630
The Mexicanos who come
here come here to work.

00:11:38.630 --> 00:11:40.970
They come here to work
and they work hard.

00:11:40.970 --> 00:11:43.550
They do jobs that
nobody else wants

00:11:43.550 --> 00:11:46.652
