And I mean, I feel like it's
good stuff that's coming.

00:32:59.340 --> 00:33:00.690
You know?

00:33:00.690 --> 00:33:04.290
I mean, I've been at
this for a lot of years,

00:33:04.290 --> 00:33:07.540
quietly just working
